<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN252-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉai avar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
  </div>
    <div xml:id="PN252">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṟaṅkuveḷ ḷaruvi yēṟṟali ṉiṟampeyarntu</l>
<l>tillai yaṉṉa pulleṉ caṭaiyō</l>
<l>ṭaḷḷilait tāḷi koyyu mōṉē</l>
<l>yilvaḻaṅku maṭamayil piṇikkuñ</l>
<l>colvalai vēṭṭuva ṉāyiṉaṉ muṉṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> He who [now] plucks sharp-leafed bindweed, (3)</l>
<l>  with matted hair empty like the blinding-tree (2)</l>
<l>  after changing colour because of receiving the roaring waterfall, (1)</l>
<l>  earlier he was a hunter with a word net (5)</l>
<l>  who ensnared innocent peacocks that roam the house. (4)</l>
</lg>
    </div>
